---
// The single spot of saturated color on the site. No Chinese glyph (spec §1).
---
<div class="inline-flex flex-col items-center gap-2 select-none">
  <div class="relative grid place-items-center w-[58px] h-[58px] rounded-[7px] -rotate-3"
       style="background: var(--seal); box-shadow: 0 3px 14px rgba(178,58,46,0.35);">
    <span class="font-display font-semibold text-[24px] tracking-tight" style="color:#f3ece0;">IT</span>
    <span class="absolute inset-[3px] rounded-[4px] border" style="border-color: rgba(243,236,224,0.35);"></span>
  </div>
  <small class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-4">for those who understand</small>
</div>
